{"tid":2392960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"拒幫雙胞胎兒戴口罩！蒼井空堅稱「3歲以下不用戴」掀爭議","createTime":"2021-02-03T06:45:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T19:22:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"723649b6546b5ac7fe2976a4cb400a9acba7fbfe","tid":2392960,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:45:01.000Z","msg":"日本前AV女優蒼井空外型甜美、身材性感，在AV界有著頗高的地位，近年她退出AV界轉戰演藝圈，直到2017年結婚生子，逐漸淡出螢光幕，但仍經常透過社群平台分享生活點滴。近日，蒼井空帶著雙胞胎兒子外出，卻被發現沒有戴口罩，遭網友指正後卻回應：「3歲以下的寶寶們不要戴。」掀起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/10/13/2825139-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F10%2F13%2F2825139-PH.jpg&h=263711f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蒼井空婚後專心在家相夫教子。（圖／翻攝自蒼井空微博）<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）肆虐全球，近來更因為變種病毒導致疫情升溫，日本政府更在1月二度發布「緊急事態宣言」。然而2日蒼井空曬出帶兒子們出門的照片，卻被發現2個兒子都沒有戴上口罩，引來網友提醒：「日本疫情也好嚴重，出門注意好防護，尤其孩子」、「口罩要戴好喔，尤其是小寶寶」、「為什麼不給寶寶戴個口罩呢？這樣不是很安全吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/03/3012776-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F3012776-PH.jpg&h=e3e61d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼蒼井空帶兒子出門，卻沒幫他們戴口罩。（圖／翻攝自蒼井空微博）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/03/3012778-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F3012778-PH.jpg&h=b1903633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n遭到網友連環逼問，蒼井空轉發自己的微博，並回應：「我戴口罩哦～3歲以下的寶寶們不要戴，還是不可以使用啊。」一番話掀起網友熱議，直說：「最好還是戴兒童口罩，還要與人保持距離」、「需要戴口罩的，不管是成人還是兒童」、「不能掉以輕心，小孩子更需要保護好」、「小朋友戴口罩實在不好受的話盡量少帶出門吧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/03/3012782-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2F3012782-PH.jpg&h=21abf1c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲蒼井空認為3歲以下不用戴口罩。（圖／翻攝自蒼井空微博）"},{"pid":"2a5ebdf48340ae8c9774e5447db77df40c5bcf71","tid":2392960,"uid":14782,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:46:54.000Z","msg":"3吋以下可以不用戴套"},{"pid":"bf84b1c9d2edd07de541f50fa4cac798179f81fb","tid":2392960,"uid":261849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"信Av 唔怕"},{"pid":"8619cc694e93321c46f6ac0dee7520ca48201f66","tid":2392960,"uid":89382,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:48:55.000Z","msg":"3歲就緊係不用戴，冇錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48d0ecad4974ad6e96aacaef1931c6a8c4936e6","tid":2392960,"uid":2002,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"都keep得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我個樣都係無咩腦"},{"pid":"fbf87ee01c4f1d5f606abc8a3abf3c99d2e4c6d2","tid":2392960,"uid":16659,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"c48d0ecad4974ad6e96aacaef1931c6a8c4936e6","tid":2392960,"uid":2002,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"都keep得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我個樣都係無咩腦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"你無咩腦?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cf7620fbbb8aeba4829b5f77e753645837cda2","tid":2392960,"uid":33359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"樓豬是基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOgBJfN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOgBJfN.png&h=69484f03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b095e0db2475d8197407f70c5667a040334ae1c7","tid":2392960,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02